      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "These clauses often reflect the risk profile of the business, but they can certainly feel overwhelming to freelancers. To protect yourself, try to ensure the scope of the indemnification is narrow and specific to things *you* directly control, like your use of third-party assets. Also, consider purchasing professional liability insurance, which can offer a safety net against unforeseen legal claims.",
